description: Returns a ProfilingGroupDescription object that contains information about the requested profiling group.

parameters.name: profilingGroupName
parameters.description: The name of the profiling group to get information about.

nested_items.name: profilingGroup
nested_items.description: The returned ProfilingGroupDescription object that contains information about the requested profiling group.

nested_items.name: agentOrchestrationConfig
nested_items.description: An AgentOrchestrationConfig object that indicates if the profiling group is enabled for profiled or not.

nested_items.name: profilingEnabled
nested_items.description: A Boolean that specifies whether the profiling agent collects profiling data or not. Set to true to enable profiling.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) identifying the profiling group resource.

nested_items.name: computePlatform
nested_items.description: The compute platform of the profiling group. If it is set to AWSLambda, then the profiled application runs on AWS Lambda. If it is set to Default, then the profiled application runs on a compute platform that is not AWS Lambda, such an Amazon EC2 instance, an on-premises server, or a different platform. The default is Default.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time when the profiling group was created. Specify using the ISO 8601 format. For example, 2020-06-01T13:15:02.001Z represents 1 millisecond past June 1, 2020 1:15:02 PM UTC.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the profiling group.

nested_items.name: profilingStatus
nested_items.description: A ProfilingStatus object that includes information about the last time a profile agent pinged back, the last time a profile was received, and the aggregation period and start time for the most recent aggregated profile.

nested_items.name: latestAgentOrchestratedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time when the profiling agent most recently pinged back. Specify using the ISO 8601 format. For example, 2020-06-01T13:15:02.001Z represents 1 millisecond past June 1, 2020 1:15:02 PM UTC.

nested_items.name: latestAgentProfileReportedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time when the most recent profile was received. Specify using the ISO 8601 format. For example, 2020-06-01T13:15:02.001Z represents 1 millisecond past June 1, 2020 1:15:02 PM UTC.

nested_items.name: latestAggregatedProfile
nested_items.description: An AggregatedProfileTime object that contains the aggregation period and start time for an aggregated profile.

nested_items.name: period
nested_items.description: The aggregation period. This indicates the period during which an aggregation profile collects posted agent profiles for a profiling group. Use one of three valid durations that are specified using the ISO 8601 format.

nested_items.name: start
nested_items.description: The time that aggregation of posted agent profiles for a profiling group starts. The aggregation profile contains profiles posted by the agent starting at this time for an aggregation period specified by the period property of the AggregatedProfileTime object.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time when the profiling group was last updated. Specify using the ISO 8601 format. For example, 2020-06-01T13:15:02.001Z represents 1 millisecond past June 1, 2020 1:15:02 PM UTC.
